snippet.title: The Sims 3 Generations Launch Trailer
snippet.description: IF TROUBLE IS OUT THERE, THEY'LL FIND IT. Everyone's up to no good in The Sims™ 3 Generations. Push your Sims further than you ever thought possible. Play with more fun. Play with more drama. Play with more mischief at every age. Available May 31st, 2011. Order your copy today at www.ThesSims3.com!
